es","50 g water","120 g red peppers, cut in bite-sized pieces","500 g large white beans, tinned (e.g. borlotti or white haricots blanc), drained"]}],"id":"r175654","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-ik6YCE8M6zI\/XZQvI3WGXDI\/AAAAAAAAcaU\/w9L53TOpjt85gh7dXDQOCr_chXZYccQqQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ByZ9iup9EW8GAlFv.png","title":"Kingclip with Chakalaka Vegetables and Dill Butter","publishedAt":"2017-08-14T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"25.4 g","fat":"20 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"19.4 g","calories":"1514.8 kJ \/ 362 kcal"},"basicInfo":["easy","30m","50m","8 portions"]}